comment_text:
My Top 10 till date: 
SEASON 1: Fish Night (haunting!), Helping Hand (chilling!!), Zima Blue (thought-provoking!), Lucky 13 (left me tearful!), Blindspot (just cool!), Suits (mech farmers vs alien insects on a bubble-wrapped planet!); 
SEASON 2: Ice (cool tints on sibling loyalty!), Pop Squad (earth in a century!);
SEASON 3: The Very Pulse of the Machine (mesmerizing!), Jibaro (he had it coming!) 😀
